description: Try our easy to follow Beef Pho To Go recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Pho,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Beef,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Beef Pho To Go Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 100g beef eye fillet, very thinly sliced

recipeInstructions.text: Combine Campbell's Bone Broth Beef, star anise and sauce in a medium saucepan. Bring to boil. Simmer for 2 minutes. Add noodles and bok choy. Simmer for a further 1 to 2 minutes. Remove from heat. Remove and discard star anise. Add beef.
Serve topped with coriander, mint, chilli, onions and bean sprouts.
